  <value column> as value,
  <series name column> as metric

ORDER BY <time_column> ASC

SELECT
  LatencyTestResults.Id
FROM LatencyTestResults, LatencyTestMeasurments, LatencyTestParameters

AND LatencyTestParameters.LatencyTestResultId = LatencyTestResults.Id 
AND LatencyTestResults.Id  = ${Test1_Id:singlequote}
GROUP BY LatencyTestResults.Id
